                <h1>Does Visiting a Dispensary Affect Your Record?</h1>
                <p>Visiting a dispensary typically does not go on your criminal record or background check. Dispensaries operate legally in many areas, and the transaction is private. However, it's essential to understand local laws regarding cannabis use, as regulations can vary widely and impact how such visits are treated.</p>
